Description: simple and modern eBook viewer.
 A simple and modern GTK+ eBook viewer, built with GJS and Epub.js.
 .
 Features include:
 - View .epub, .mobi, .azw, and .azw3 files in two-page view or scrolled view
 - Customize font, line-spacing, margins, and brightness
 - Light, sepia, dark, and invert mode, or add your own custom themes
 - Reading progress slider with chapter marks
 - Bookmarks and annotations
 - Find in book
 - Quick dictionary lookup with Wiktionary, Wikipedia, and `dictd`, or translate
   text with Google Translate
 - Touchpad gesturesâ€”use two-finger swipe to turn the page
 - Basic text-to-speech support with eSpeak and Festival (suggested packages)
  .
 More features can be enabled by installing the suggested packages, including
 hyphenation.
